  <name>Schnelle Umlaute</name>
  <summary>Quick German umlaut input</summary>
  <description>
    <p>
      Input German umlauts (ä, ö, ü, ß) by holding the base letter and pressing Space.
      Hold 'a' + Space → ä
      Hold 'o' + Space → ö
      Hold 'u' + Space → ü
      Hold 's' + Space → ß

      Works in X11 and Wayland without clipboard or root permissions.
    </p>
  </description>
